'''1984年罗杰尼希教生物恐怖攻击'''（{{lang|en|1984 Rajneeshee bioterror attack}}）是一场发生在[[美国|美国]][[俄勒冈州|俄勒冈州]][[沃斯科县|沃斯科县]]达尔斯的[[生物恐怖主义|生物恐怖袭击]]，[[奥修|罗杰尼希教]]（奧修教）领导小组蓄意向当地十家[[餐馆|餐馆]]投放鼠伤寒[[肠道沙门氏菌|沙门氏菌]]，目的是令当地选民无法投票，以便该组织候选人能在1984年沃斯科县选举中胜出。事件导致751人[[食物中毒|食物中毒]]，其中45人需入院治疗，但無人丧生<ref name="flaccus">{{cite news | last =Flaccus | first =Gillian | title =Ore. Town Never Recovered From Scare | agency =Associated Press | date =2001-10-19 | url =http://www.culteducation.com/reference/rajneesh/rajneesh8.html | accessdate =2014-02-20 | archivedate =2014-02-20 | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20140220033714/http://www.culteducation.com/reference/rajneesh/rajneesh8.html | deadurl =no }}</ref>。这是美国历史上的第一次，也是最大规模的一次生物恐怖攻击<ref name="healthexperts">{{cite news | last =Scripps Howard News Service | title =Health experts fear bioterror attack | work =Grand Rapids Press | page =G1 | date =2007-01-28 | quote = A total of 751 people, including members of the Wasco County Commission, became ill with nausea, diarrhea, headaches and fever. Forty-five people were hospitalized, but no one died. It was the first, and still the largest, germ-warfare attack in U.S. history.}}</ref><ref name="lewis">{{cite web | last =Lewis | first =Susan K | title =History of Biowarfare: Bioterror, The Cults | work =Nova Online Website | publisher =WGBH/NOVA | date =2001-11 | url =http://www.pbs.org/wgbh/nova/bioterror/hist_nf.html#cult | accessdate =2014-02-19 | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20140103132513/http://www.pbs.org/wgbh/nova/bioterror/hist_nf.html#cult | archivedate =2014-01-03 | deadurl =no }}</ref>。這也是自1945年以来，经过确认仅有的两次恐怖分子使用[[生物武器|生物武器]]危害人类的事件之一<ref name="wheelis">{{cite book | last1=Wheelis | first1=Mark | url=http://www.amazon.com/Deadly-Cultures-Biological-Weapons-since/dp/0674016998 | last2=Rózsa | first2=Lajos | last3=Dando | first3=Malcolm | title=Deadly Cultures: Biological Weapons Since 1945 | publisher=Harvard University Press | year=2006 | pages=284-293, 301-303 | isbn=0-674-01699-8 | accessdate=2014-02-20 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130702055325/http://www.amazon.com/Deadly-Cultures-Biological-Weapons-since/dp/0674016998 | archivedate=2013-07-02 | deadurl=no }}</ref>。

罗杰尼希的追随者早前已取得了沃斯科县小镇{{link-en|安蒂洛普 (俄勒冈州)|Antelope, Oregon|安蒂洛普}}的政治控制权，他们以附近的[[奥修庄园城|奥修庄园城]]为基地，希望能在1984年11月的选举中赢得沃斯科县巡回法院的两到三个席位。达尔斯市不但是沃斯科县的县城，而且也是人口最多的城市。由于担心未能获得足够选票，奥修庄园城的官员决定毒害达尔斯市的选民，他们起初把鼠伤寒沙门氏菌混在水杯裡向两名县委员下毒，然后再大范围地在当地餐馆的沙拉吧和沙拉酱中投放。

俄勒冈州公共卫生部和[[美国疾病控制与预防中心|美国疾病控制与预防中心]]进行的初步调查没有排除蓄意污染的可能性，但实际的污染源头是在一年后才发现的。1985年2月28日，该州[[民主党_(美国)|民主党]][[联邦众议员|联邦众议员]]{{link-en|詹姆斯·H·韦弗|James H. Weaver}}在联邦众议院发表演说，“指控罗杰尼希教向八家餐馆的沙拉吧配料中喷灑培植的沙门氏菌”<ref name="nytimesweaver">{{cite news | last =Weaver | first =James | title =Slow Medical Sleuthing | work =The New York Times | publisher =The New York Times Company | date =2001-04-24 | url =http://www.nytimes.com/2001/04/24/science/l-slow-medical-sleuthing-003751.html | accessdate =2014-02-19 | quote =I accused the Rajneeshees of sprinkling salmonella culture on salad bar ingredients in eight restaurants. | archivedate =2014-01-06 | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20140106054034/http://www.nytimes.com/2001/04/24/science/l-slow-medical-sleuthing-003751.html | deadurl =no }}</ref>。在1985年9月的一次记者招待会上，罗杰尼希本人指控自己的多名支持者涉嫌包括这次恐怖攻击在内的多起犯罪事件，其中还包括1985年一场刺杀联邦检察官但已经流产的计划，请求州和[[美国联邦政府|联邦政府]]展开调查<ref name="gordon">{{cite book | last =Gordon | first =James S. | title =The Golden Guru – The Strange Journey of Bhagwan Shree Rajneesh | publisher =The Stephen Greene Press | year =1987 | pages =181-182 | id = | isbn =0-8289-0630-0 | url =http://www.amazon.com/Golden-Guru-Strange-Journey-Rajneesh/dp/0828906300 | accessdate =2014-02-20 | archivedate =2013-06-30 | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20130630225211/http://www.amazon.com/Golden-Guru-Strange-Journey-Rajneesh/dp/0828906300 | deadurl =no }}</ref>。[[俄勒冈州总检察长|俄勒冈州总检察长]]{{link-en|大卫·B·弗朗麦尔|David B. Frohnmayer}}成立了一个由俄勒冈州州警和[[联邦调查局|联邦调查局]]等多个部门组成的跨机构工作组，获得搜查令和传票后对奥修庄园城展开搜查，在一間医学实验室内发现了与达尔斯居民感染提取样本相符的細菌。最终两名奥修庄园城的主要官员被起诉，他们在最低设防级别的联邦监狱中服刑29个月后获释。

== 策划 ==
[[File:Osho_Drive_By.jpg|thumb]]坐在自己豪华的[[劳斯莱斯|劳斯莱斯]]中，向正处于[[弃绝期|弃绝期]]的追随者打招呼，这是他在奥修庄园城的日常公事，照片摄于1982年。]]

自1981年開始，成千上万的罗杰尼希追随者搬到沃斯科县乡下的“大泥泞农场”（{{lang|en|Big Muddy Ranch}}），在这里建立起[[奥修庄园城|奥修庄园城]]<ref name="snow">{{cite book | last =Snow | first =Robert L. | title =Deadly Cults: The Crimes of True Believers | publisher =Praeger/Greenwood | url =http://www.amazon.com/Deadly-Cults-Crimes-True-Believers/dp/0275980529 | accessdate =2014-02-20 | archivedate =2013-06-29 | year =2003 | pages =87-90 | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20130629055642/http://www.amazon.com/Deadly-Cults-Crimes-True-Believers/dp/0275980529 | deadurl =no | isbn =0-275-98052-9 }}</ref><ref name="fitzgerald">{{cite book | last =FitzGerald | first =Frances | title =Cities on a Hill | url =https://archive.org/details/citiesonhill00fitz | publisher =Simon & Schuster | year =1987 | pages =[https://archive.org/details/citiesonhill00fitz/page/360 360]-361, 378 | id = | isbn =0-671-55209-0 }}</ref>。他们很快获得了附近人口仅有75的小镇安蒂洛普的政治控制权，并将之更名为“罗杰尼希”（{{lang|en|Rajneesh}}）<ref name="thompson">{{cite book | last =Thompson | first =Christopher M. | title =The Bioterrorism Threat By Non-State Actors: "The Rajneeshee Cult" | publisher =United States Navy | date =2006-12 | pages =17-30 | url =http://www.ccc.nps.navy.mil/research/theses/thompson06.pdf | format =PDF | accessdate =2009-03-26 | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20090326082738/http://www.ccc.nps.navy.mil/research/theses/thompson06.pdf | archivedate =2009-03-26 | deadurl =yes }}</ref>。这些信徒起初与当地居民相处友好，但由于当地人对其公社的扩张反应冷淡，关系很快转朝负面发展<ref name="thompson" />。申请奥修庄园城的建设许可证遭拒后，社区领导人决定通过影响1984年11月的县选举来获得该县其他地区的政治控制权<ref name="fitzgerald" />。他们的目标是赢得沃斯科县巡回[[法院|法院]]两到三个席位和县警长的职位<ref name="flaccus" />。为了左右这场[[选举|选举]]，他们启动了一个“共享家园”（{{lang|en|Share-a-Home}}）方案，把成千上万无家可归的人运到奥修庄园城，以求大幅增加支持该组织[[候选人|候选人]]的选民数量<ref name="carus">{{cite book | last =Carus | first =W. Seth | title =Bioterrorism and Biocrimes | publisher =The Minerva Group, Inc. | year =2002 | pages =50-55 | url =http://www.fas.org/irp/threat/cbw/carus.pdf | format =PDF | id = | isbn =1-4101-0023-5 | accessdate =2014-02-19 | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20131029191051/http://www.fas.org/irp/threat/cbw/carus.pdf | archivedate =2013-10-29 | deadurl =no }}</ref><ref name="carter">{{cite book | last =Carter | first =Lewis F. | title =Charisma and Control in Rajneeshpuram | url =http://www.amazon.com/Charisma-Control-Rajneeshpuram-Sociological-Association/dp/0521135133 | publisher =Cambridge University Press | year =1990 | page =202-238 | isbn =0-521-38554-7 | archivedate =2013-06-28 | deadurl =no | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20130628125426/http://www.amazon.com/Charisma-Control-Rajneeshpuram-Sociological-Association/dp/0521135133 | access-date =2014-02-20 }}</ref>。但是，沃斯科县通过强制要求所有新选民在登记时证明自己的选民资格，使奥修庄园城的计划流產<ref name="entis">{{cite book | last =Entis | first =Phyllis | title =Food Safety: Old Habits, New Perspectives | publisher =Blackwell Publishing | year =2007 | pages =244-246 | isbn =1-55581-417-4 | url =http://www.amazon.com/Food-Safety-Old-Habits-Perspectives/dp/1555814174 | accessdate =2014-02-20 | archivedate =2013-06-30 | deadurl =no | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20130630210455/http://www.amazon.com/Food-Safety-Old-Habits-Perspectives/dp/1555814174 }}</ref>。

社区的领导人于是密謀使居住在达尔斯的选民无法參與投票，以左右沃斯科县的选举结果<ref name="grossman">{{cite news | last =Grossman | first =Lawrence K. | title =The Story of a Truly Contaminated Election | work =Columbia Journalism Review | date =2001-01 | archivedate =2008-11-19 | deadurl =yes | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20081119154050/http://backissues.cjrarchives.org/year/01/1/grossman.asp | url =http://backissues.cjrarchives.org/year/01/1/grossman.asp | accessdate =2008-11-19 }}</ref>。约有12人参与了获取生物制剂的密谋，至少11人涉及了事件策划<ref name="carus" />。参与奥修庄园城医学实验室开发的人应该不超过四人，不过并不一定所有人都知道自己的工作将会用于什么样的目标<ref name="carus" />。至少有八人参与了实际投毒<ref name="carus" />。这场攻击的主要策划者包括罗杰尼希的首席副官兼私人[[秘书|秘书]][[玛·阿南德·席拉|玛·阿南德·席拉]]和罗杰尼希医药公司财务部长黛安·伊冯娜·奥南（{{lang|en|Diane Yvonne Onang}}），其中后者是个执业[[护士|护士]]<ref name="carus" /><ref name="miller">{{cite book |last1=Miller |url=http://www.amazon.com/Germs-Biological-Weapons-Americas-Secret/dp/0684871599 |first1=Judith |last2=Broad |first2=William |last3=Engelberg |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105210857/http://www.amazon.com/Germs-Biological-Weapons-Americas-Secret/dp/0684871599 |archivedate=2013-11-05 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2014-02-20 |first3=Stephen |title=Germs: Biological Weapons and America's Secret War |publisher=Simon & Schuster |date=2002-09-17 |pages=1-34: "The Attack" |id= |isbn=0-684-87159-9 }}</ref>。沙门氏菌是从[[华盛顿州|华盛顿州]][[西雅图|西雅图]]的一家医疗用品公司购买的，然后在社区内的实验室加以培养<ref name="carus" />。对餐馆沙拉吧进行投毒被认为只是一次“试验性操作”<ref name="carter" /><ref>{{cite book | last =Board on Global Health, Forum on Microbial Threats, Institute of Medicine | title =Addressing Foodborne Threats to Health: Policies, Practices, and Global Coordination | publisher =National Academies | year =2006 | pages =39, 41 | isbn =0-309-10043-7 | url =http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21850788 | accessdate =2014-02-20 | archive-date =2019-06-28 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20190628233635/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/21850788 | dead-url =no }}</ref>，该组织还曾试图将[[病原体|病原体]]释放到达尔斯的供水系统中<ref name="carus" />。如果这一企图成功，该组织还计划在更接近[[选举日_(美国)|选举日]]时故伎重演<ref name="carter" />。第二部分的计划从未付诸实行<ref name="carter" />，因为公社在确认“共享家园”计划将因新人不能投票而失效后决定抵制这场选举<ref name="carter" />。

== 下毒 ==
[[File:WascoCountyCourthouse.jpg|thumb]]
[[File:TheDallesTacoTimeSalsaBar.jpg|thumb]]吧台。]]
1984年8月29日，两名沃斯科县委员访问奥修庄园城，接待人员在他们飲用的食水中加入沙门氏菌，导致两人中毒，其中一人需要住院治疗。<ref name="wheelis" />随后，席拉一组的成员把沙门氏菌散布到杂货店以及县法院的门把手和小便器的手柄上，但这没有达到他们预期的效果<ref name="wheelis" />。1984年9月至10月，他们在当地十家餐馆投放沙门氏菌，共计751人受感染<ref name="urbano">{{cite book | last =Urbano | first =Mary Theresa | title =The Complete Bioterrorism Survival Guide | url =https://archive.org/details/completebioterro0000urba | publisher =Sentient Publications | year =2006 | pages =[https://archive.org/details/completebioterro0000urba/page/60 60]-61 | isbn = 1-59181-051-5}}</ref>，當中45人需要住院治疗，不过所有人都成功脱险<ref>{{cite book | last1=Schweitzer | first1=Glenn E. | last2=Schweitzer |first2=Carole Dorsch | title =A Faceless Enemy: The Origins of Modern Terrorism | url=https://archive.org/details/facelessenemyori0000schw | publisher =Da Capo Press | year =2002 | page =[https://archive.org/details/facelessenemyori0000schw/page/121 121] | isbn = 0-7382-0757-8}}</ref>。

该组织使用的主要投毒方法是由一位成员将一袋含有沙门氏菌的淡棕色液体偷偷带进餐馆，然后要么将其喷灑到沙拉吧的食品上，要么将之倒入沙拉酱<ref name="mccann">{{cite book | last =McCann | first =Joseph T. | title =Terrorism on American Soil: A Concise History of Plots and Perpetrators from the Famous to the Forgotten | url =https://archive.org/details/terrorismonameri00jose | publisher =Sentient Publications | year =2006 | pages =[https://archive.org/details/terrorismonameri00jose/page/151 151]-158 | isbn = 1-59181-049-3}}</ref>。肇事者把这种液体称为[[萨尔萨辣酱|萨尔萨辣酱]]<ref name="miller" />。截止1984年9月24日，已有超过150人感到严重不适<ref name="garrett" />。到了9月底，当地出現751宗急性[[肠胃炎|肠胃炎]]個案，实验结果显示所有受害者都感染了鼠伤寒沙门氏菌<ref name="garrett">{{cite book | last =Garrett | first =Laurie | title =Betrayal of Trust: The Collapse of Global Public Health | url =https://archive.org/details/betrayaloftrustc00garr | publisher =Hyperion | year =2000 | location =New York | pages =[https://archive.org/details/betrayaloftrustc00garr/page/540 540]-541, 544 | isbn = 0-7868-8440-1}}</ref>。发病症状包括[[腹泻|腹泻]]、[[发烧|发烧]]、发冷、[[恶心|恶心]]、[[呕吐|呕吐]]、头痛、腹痛和便血<ref name="urbano" />。受害者的年龄中最小的是从[[母亲|母亲]]处传染到病菌的出生仅两天的婴儿，起初[[医生|医生]]诊断其存活率只有5%<ref name="carter" />；最大的则已是87岁高龄<ref name="snow" />。

当地居民怀疑罗杰尼希的追随者是投毒事件的幕后主腦，并成群结队地在选举日当天前往投票，防止该组织赢得任何县级公职，从而挫败了这場恐怖主义阴谋<ref name="flaccus" />。罗杰尼希教的候选人最终退出了1984年11月的选举<ref name="mccann" />。整个公社的7,000名教众中仅有239人參與投票<ref>{{cite news |author=UPI Staff |title=Few Followers of Guru Vote |work=The New York Times |publisher=The New York Times Company |date=1984-11-09 |url=http://www.nytimes.com/1984/11/09/us/few-followers-of-guru-vote.html |accessdate=2014-02-19 |archivedate=2014-01-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140106042456/http://www.nytimes.com/1984/11/09/us/few-followers-of-guru-vote.html |deadurl=no }}</ref>。这场疫情给当地餐饮业造成数十万[[美元|美元]]的损失，卫生部门关闭了受影响区域的沙拉吧<ref name="flaccus" />。一些居民由于担心会有进一步的攻击而不敢独自出门<ref>{{cite book | last =Stripling | first =Mahala Yates | title =Bioethics And Medical Issues In Literature | publisher =Greenwood Press | year =2005 | page =24 | isbn =0-313-32040-3 | url =http://www.amazon.com/Bioethics-Medical-Literature-Exploring-through/dp/0313320403 | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20130629050214/http://www.amazon.com/Bioethics-Medical-Literature-Exploring-through/dp/0313320403 | archivedate =2013-06-29 | deadurl =no | accessdate =2014-02-20 }}</ref>。一位居民表示：“人们都很害怕，都吓坏了。他们不敢出门，不敢单独外出，人们都成了囚犯（把自己关在家里）。”<ref name="snow" />

== 调查 ==
多个不同部门派出官员和调查人员前往达尔斯，对爆發疫情的原因展开调查<ref name="grossman" />。当时的俄勒冈州公共卫生实验室主任迈克尔·斯基尔斯博士（{{lang|en|Dr. Michael Skeels}}）表示，事件引发如此大规模的公共卫生调查是因为，“这是美国1984年出现的最大一起食品相关疫情。”<ref name="garrett" />调查确定致病病菌为鼠伤寒沙门氏菌，其结论认为疫情爆发是由於餐馆工作人员的个人卫生情况太差，因为这些工作人员在大多数顾客生病前自己就已经病倒了<ref name="miller" /><ref name="novick">{{cite book | url =http://www.amazon.com/Public-Health-Issues-Disaster-Preparedness/dp/0763725005 | last =Novick | first =Lloyd | title =Public Health Issues Disaster Preparedness: Focus on Bioterrorism | publisher =Jones and Bartlett Publishers | year =2003 | pages =90, 104, 113 | id = | isbn =0-7637-2500-5 | accessdate =2014-02-20 | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20130705161912/http://www.amazon.com/Public-Health-Issues-Disaster-Preparedness/dp/0763725005 | archivedate =2013-07-05 | deadurl =no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last =Staff | title =Ill Handlers Suspected in Oregon Food Poisonings | work =The New York Times | publisher =The New York Times Company | date =1984-10-21 | url =http://www.nytimes.com/1984/10/21/us/ill-handlers-suspected-in-oregon-food-poisonings.html | accessdate =2014-02-19 | archivedate =2012-11-11 | deadurl =no | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20121111121457/http://www.nytimes.com/1984/10/21/us/ill-handlers-suspected-in-oregon-food-poisonings.html }}</ref>。

俄勒冈州民主党联邦众议员詹姆斯·H·韦弗認為官方结论还不足以充分解释疫情，因此继续进行调查<ref name="carter" />。他联系了[[美国疾病控制与预防中心|美国疾病控制与预防中心]]和其他机构的医师，促请他们对罗杰尼希教进行调查<ref name="nytimesweaver" /><ref name="carter" />。据刘易斯·F·卡特（{{lang|en|Lewis F. Carter}}）所著《奥修庄园城的魅力和操控》（{{lang|en|''Charisma and Control in Rajneeshpuram''}}）中的说法，许多人都把韦弗的担忧视为一种偏执，或是对罗杰尼希教存在典型的偏见<ref name="carter" />。1985年2月28日，韦弗在联邦众议院发表演说，“指控罗杰尼希教向八家餐馆的沙拉吧配料中喷灑培值的沙门氏菌”<ref name="nytimesweaver" /><ref name="weavercongress">{{cite journal | last =Weaver | first =James | title =The Town That Was Poisoned | journal =Congressional Record | volume =131 | issue =3-4 | pages =4185-4189, 99th United States Congress, 1st Session | publisher =United States Government Printing Office | location =Washington, D.C. | date =1985-02-28 | url =http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/Image:1985_Feb_28_Congressman_Weaver_THE_TOWN_THAT_WAS_POISONED.pdf | format =PDF | accessdate =2008-10-29 | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20081029205105/http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/08/1985_Feb_28_Congressman_Weaver_THE_TOWN_THAT_WAS_POISONED.pdf | archivedate =2008-10-29 | deadurl =yes }} Transcription at [https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/The_Town_That_Was_Poisoned/Congressman_Weaver WikiSource] {{Wayback|url=https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/The_Town_That_Was_Poisoned/Congressman_Weaver |date=20201109033656 }}</ref>。事件之后的发展证明了韦弗的论断，他提出的虽然都是间接证据，但理据充分，调查人员几个月后对奥修庄园城进行调查所发现的证据充分证实了他对罗杰尼希教的看法<ref name="carter" />。

1985年9月16日，因自我孤立而沉寂四年的巴关·希瑞·罗杰尼希本人出现在追随者的公社<ref name="miller" /><ref name="nytimesroiled" />，并召开了多场记者招待会，声称席拉和包括奥南在内的共计20位公社领袖在上个[[周末|周末]]离开奥修庄园城前往[[欧洲|欧洲]]<ref name="gordon" /><ref name="nytimesroiled">{{cite news | last =Martin | first =Douglas | title =Guru's Commune Roiled As Key Leader Departs | work =The New York Times | publisher =The New York Times Company | date =1985-09-22 | archivedate =2014-01-06 | deadurl =no | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20140106122031/http://www.nytimes.com/1985/09/22/us/guru-s-commune-roiled-as-key-leader-departs.html | url =http://www.nytimes.com/1985/09/22/us/guru-s-commune-roiled-as-key-leader-departs.html | accessdate =2014-02-19 }}</ref>。他还表示，自己在这20人离开后从其他教众处得知，席拉等人犯下了一系列的严重罪行<ref name="fitzgerald" /><ref name="nytimesroiled" />。罗杰尼希称席拉等人为“[[法西斯主义|法西斯主义]]黑帮”，称他们还曾试图毒害自己的医生和女伴，以及[[杰佛逊县_(俄勒冈州)|杰佛逊县]]的地区检察官，甚至向达西斯的供水系统投毒<ref name="fitzgerald" />。他还补充道，自己相信这伙人已经向一位县委员和[[法官|法官]]威廉·赫尔斯（{{lang|en|William Hulse}}）下过毒，并且他们有可能一手导致了达尔斯的疫情爆发<ref name="fitzgerald" />，并邀请州和联邦政府前来奥修庄园城展开调查<ref name="miller" />。外界人士起初对他的说法抱持怀疑态度<ref name="nytimesroiled" />。

俄勒冈州总检察长大卫·{{lang|en|B}}·弗朗麦尔成立了一个由沃斯科县警长办公室、俄勒冈州州警、联邦调查局、[[美国移民及归化局|美国移民及归化局]]以及[[美国国民警卫队|国民警卫队]]组成的跨机构工作组来到农场，并在农场设立总部，对罗杰尼斯的指控进行调查<ref name="miller" />。为避免证据被销毁，工作组取得了[[搜查令|搜查令]]和传票，50位调查人员于1985年10月2日进入农场<ref name="miller" />。斯基尔斯博士在奥修庄园城医疗诊所的实验室发现了含有沙门氏菌的玻璃瓶<ref name="miller" />。经美国疾病控制与预防中心位于[[亚特兰大|亚特兰大]]的实验室分析后证实，罗杰尼希实验室的细菌样本和在当地餐馆就餐后患病的个人所感染的细菌完全一致<ref name="miller" />。这次调查还发现罗杰尼希教在1984和1985年先后进行过多次毒药、化学品和细菌的实验<ref name="miller" />。斯基尔斯博士描绘自己在罗杰尼斯实验室看到的情景就像是“一个用于大批量生产微生物的细菌学冷冻机”<ref name="garrett" />。调查人员还发现了一本《[[无政府主义者食谱|无政府主义者食谱]]》（{{lang|en|''The Anarchist Cookbook''}}），该书上介绍了炸药和军用生化武器的制造和使用<ref name="garrett" />。调查者认为，该组织之前已在俄勒冈州的[[塞勒姆_(俄勒冈州)|塞勒姆]]和[[波特兰_(俄勒冈州)|波特兰]]等多个[[城市|城市]]发动过类似袭击<ref name="miller" />。之后被捕的策划者在证词中宣称，他们曾攻击过一家疗养院以及中哥伦比亚医疗中心的一个沙拉吧，但这些没有在法庭上得以证实<ref name="miller" />。执法人员还发现罗杰尼希教曾于1985年试图[[谋杀|谋杀]]俄勒冈州前联邦检查官查尔斯·H·特纳（{{lang|en|Charles H. Turner}}），但这一密谋最终没有实施<ref>{{cite news | url =http://www.culteducation.com/reference/rajneesh/rajneesh6.html | last =Larabee | first =Mark | title =Two Rajneeshee members plead guilty: Sally-Anne Croft and Susan Hagan return to the United States to face 15-year-old wiretapping charges | work =The Oregonian | date =2000-12-16 | accessdate =2014-02-20 | archive-date =2014-03-01 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20140301174905/http://www.culteducation.com/reference/rajneesh/rajneesh6.html | dead-url =no }}</ref>。

== 起诉 ==
[[File:1982_Osho_driving.jpg|thumb]]（摄于1982年）。席拉声称罗杰尼希也参与了密谋，但这从未得到证实。<ref name="carus" />]]

奥修庄园城市长大卫·贝瑞·克纳普（{{lang|en|David Berry Knapp}}）主动与执法部门合作，将自己所知道的沙门氏菌攻击细节告知联邦调查局。他声称席拉“曾与罗杰尼希讨论过通过让居民生病来减少达尔斯投票选民数量的阴谋。席拉说（罗杰尼希）表示最好是不要伤害到他人，但要是只死少数几个人的话倒不用担心”<ref name="carus" />。不过根据[[朱迪思·米勒|朱迪思·米勒]]所著的《细菌：生物武器和美国的秘密战争》（{{lang|en|''Germs: Biological Weapons and America's Secret War''}}）一书中记载，这些话是席拉所说的<ref name="miller" />。克纳普的证词中还表示，席拉向对她说法表示怀疑的人播放了一卷磁带，其中有罗杰尼希的声音说道：“如果有必要做这些事情来维护（我的）愿景，那就去做吧，”以此说明在罗杰尼希的名义下，谋杀也是可以接受的，告诉那些心有疑虑者“不用担心”少数人的死，不过这卷磁带中的声音很沉闷，并不清晰<ref name="miller" />。调查还发现一份日期为1984年9月25日，来自[[美国典型培养物保藏中心|美国典型培养物保藏中心]]的微生物发票，显示奥修庄园城的实验室定购了一批鼠伤寒沙门氏菌，这种细菌可以导致威胁性命的[[伤寒|伤寒]]<ref name="miller" /><ref name="frost">{{cite book | last =Frost | first =Robin M. | title =Nuclear Terrorism After 9/11 | url =https://archive.org/details/nuclearterrorism0000fros | publisher =Routledge | year =2005 | page=[https://archive.org/details/nuclearterrorism0000fros/page/52 52] | isbn = 0-415-39992-0}}</ref>。

根据1994年刊登在《宗教社会学》（{{lang|en|''Sociology of Religion''}}）期刊上的一份研究结果，“大多数门徒表示他们相信（罗杰尼希）对玛·阿南德·席拉的非法活动是知情的”<ref name="latkin">{{cite journal | last =Latkin | first =Carl A. | author2 =Sundberg, Norman D.; Littman, Richard A.; Katsikis, Melissa G.; Hagan, Richard A. | title =Feelings after the fall: former Rajneeshpuram Commune members' perceptions of and affiliation with the Rajneeshee movement | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_sociology-of-religion_spring-1994_55_1/page/65 | journal =Sociology of Religion | volume =55 | issue =1 | pages =65-74 | doi =10.2307/3712176 | year =1994 | jstor =3712176 | publisher =Oxford University Press }}</ref>。记者弗朗西丝·菲茨杰拉德（{{lang|en|Frances FitzGerald}}）在《山上的城市》中写道，大部分罗杰尼希的追随者“相信（他）不会，也无法同意使用暴力手段去对付他人”，并且几乎所有教众都觉得这一罪行是席拉的责任，並相信罗杰尼希对此一无所知<ref name="fitzgerald" />。W·赛斯·卡鲁斯在文章中写道：“我们没有任何办法来确知（罗杰尼希）对实际决策到底有什么程度的了解。他的追随者相信他参与了席拉做出的每一个重要决策，但这些指控从未得到证实。”<ref name="tucker">{{cite book | last =Tucker | first =Jonathan B. (Ed.) | author2 = Seth W. Carus (section) | title =Toxic Terror: Assessing Terrorist Use of Chemical and Biological Weapons | publisher =MIT Press | year =2000 | pages =115-138 |isbn = 0-262-70071-9 |quote=There is no way to know to what extent [Rajneesh] participated in actual decision-making. His followers believed he was involved in every important decision that Sheela made, but those allegations were never proven.}}</ref>罗杰尼希本人坚称，席拉是他在自我孤立期间唯一的信息来源，她利用自己的位置把“一个法西斯国家”强加到公社之上<ref name="nytimesroiled" />。不过他也承认，自己的沉寂正是席拉达到目的的关键因素<ref name="nytimesroiled" />。

1985年10月27日，罗杰尼希乘飞机离开俄勒冈州，但在[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]的[[夏洛特_(北卡罗莱纳州)|夏洛特]]降落時就被[[拘捕令|拘捕]]，并受到35项蓄意违反移民法的指控<ref name="occultism">{{cite news | last =Staff | title =Bhagwan Shree Rajneesh | work =Encyclopedia of Occultism and Parapsychology, 5th ed. | publisher =Gale Group | year =2001 }}</ref><ref name="bernett">{{cite book | last =Bernett | first =Brian C. | title =U.S. Biodefense and Homeland Security Toward Detection and Attribution | publisher =United States Navy | date =2006-12 | pages =13-35: "The Rajneeshee Cult Biological Attacks" | url =http://www.ccc.nps.navy.mil/research/theses/bernett06.pdf | format =PDF | accessdate =2009-03-26 | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20090326082743/http://www.ccc.nps.navy.mil/research/theses/bernett06.pdf | archivedate =2009-03-26 | deadurl =yes }}</ref><ref name="gale03">{{cite news | title =Acharya Rajneesh | work =Contemporary Authors Online | publisher =Thomson Gale | date =2003-09-05}}</ref>。他在其中两项对移民局官员[[作出虚假陈述|作出虚假陈述]]的指控上认罪，这也是他辩诉交易协议的一部分<ref name="carter" /><ref name="mccann" /><ref name="bernett" />。法院判决他十年[[缓刑|缓刑]]、40万美元罚金，并将他驱逐出境，今后五年内不得进入美国<ref name="carter" /><ref name="gale03" /><ref name="immigrationandcustoms">{{cite news | last =Staff | title =Leadership, Director, Office of Policy and Planning, Joseph R. Greene | work =U.S. Immigration and Customs Enforcement | publisher =ICE | date =2006-09-25 | url =http://www.ice.gov/about/leadership/ot_bio/joe_greene.htm | deadurl =yes | archivedate =2007-07-19 | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20070719015322/http://www.ice.gov/about/leadership/ot_bio/joe_greene.htm | accessdate =2007-07-19 }}</ref>。他一直都没有受到与这次沙门氏菌投毒事件相关的罪名指控<ref name="carter" /><ref name="mccann" />。

1985年10月28日，席拉和奥南在[[西德|西德]]被捕。经过一段时间的磋商，两人于1986年2月6日被引渡回美国，并在波特兰受到拘捕<ref name="carter" />。指控他们的罪名包括：企图谋杀罗杰尼希的私人医生；一级攻击：毒害法官威廉·赫尔斯；二级攻击：毒害达尔斯市政委员雷蒙德·马修斯（{{lang|en|Raymond Matthews}}）；以及非法入境、窃听和在达尔斯投毒<ref name="wheelis" /><ref name="carter" />。联邦检察官办公室处理涉及十家餐馆投毒案件的起诉，而俄勒冈州总检察长办公室则起诉对马修斯和赫尔斯的毒害案<ref name="bernett" />。

1986年7月22日，两位被告决定启用[[阿尔福德条款|阿尔福德条款]]，对沙门氏菌投毒和其他指控采取有罪辩诉，以求获得从轻处罚。她们罪名的刑期范围从3年到20年不等，可以同时服刑。席拉因企图谋杀罗杰尼希的私人医生而获刑20年，毒害法官威廉·赫尔斯的一级攻击罪再获刑20年，毒害达尔斯市政委员雷蒙德·马修斯的二级攻击罪获刑10年，因在沙门氏菌投毒中扮演的角色获刑4年半，窃听阴谋再获刑4年半，还有移民欺诈被判5年缓刑；奥南则分别因上述前四宗罪名获刑15年、15年、7年半，4年半，还因窃听阴谋被判3年缓刑<ref name="wheelis" /><ref name="carter" /><ref name="bernett" />。之后两人都在最低设防级别的联邦监狱中服刑29个月后因表现良好而提前获释<ref name="wheelis" /><ref name="carter" /><ref name="senior">{{cite news | last =Senior | first =Jeanie | title = Anand Sheela tends patients in Switzerland: The former spokeswoman for Bhagwan Shree Rajneesh works in two private nursing homes | work = The Oregonian | date =1999-12-26}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last =Suo | first =Steve | title =Ex-Rajneeshee pleads guilty in conspiracy | work =Oregon Live | date =2002-12-21}}</ref>。席拉遭驱逐出境，前往[[瑞士|瑞士]]经营两家[[疗养院|疗养院]]<ref name="senior00">{{cite news | last1=Senior | first1=Jeanie | last2=Hogan | first2=Dave | title = Indian guru follower Anand Sheela arrested after German TV show: Bhagwan Shree Rajneesh's former spokeswoman is freed because a Swiss court already convicted her in 1999 | work =The Oregonian | date =2000-01-22}}</ref>。

