《[[俄勒冈人报|俄勒冈人报]]》（{{lang|en|''The Oregonian''}}）从1985年6月开始连续刊登了20期针对罗杰尼希及其组织的报道，因此就包括对这起沙门氏菌投毒事件的调查<ref name="grossman" />。随着之后的追踪调查，《俄勒冈人报》发现，他们的其中一位[[调查报导|调查记者]]莱斯利·L·再兹（{{lang|en|Leslie L. Zaitz}}）已经在席拉团体前十暗杀名单中名列第三位<ref name="grossman" />。当时的俄勒冈州总检察长大卫·B·弗朗麦尔这样评价该团体：“罗杰尼希教犯下了一系列美国历史上最令人发指的罪行……最大规模的单一婚姻欺诈事件，最庞大的窃听方案，以及最大范围的集体投毒。”<ref name="snow" /><ref name="graham">{{cite news | last =Graham | first =Rachel | title =The Saffron Swami | work =Willamette Week |edition=25th Anniversary Issue |year=1983}}</ref>回想此事，斯基尔斯表示：“这件事情让我们失去了自己的纯真……我们真的学会要变得更加多疑……第一起针对美国社会的大规模生物攻击不是由什么偷渡到纽约的外国恐怖分子发起，而是由美国社会中的合法居民启动。下一次可能会有更加致命的药剂……我们在公共卫生领域真的还没有准备好面对这一切。”<ref name="garrett" />

米尔顿·莱滕贝格尔（{{lang|en|Milton Leitenberg}}）在自己2005年的著作《评估生物武器和生物恐怖主义威胁》（{{lang|en|''Assessing the Biological Weapons and Bioterrorism Threat''}}）中指出，“显然，还没有其他任何已知的‘恐怖主义’组织成功培养了任何病原体”<ref name="leitenberg">{{cite book | last =Leitenberg | first =Milton | title =Assessing the Biological Weapons and Bioterrorism Threat | publisher =Strategic Studies Institute | date =2005-12-01 | url =http://www.strategicstudiesinstitute.army.mil/pubs/display.cfm?PubID=639 | isbn =1-4289-1626-1 | accessdate =2014-02-20 | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20140106032840/http://www.strategicstudiesinstitute.army.mil/pubs/display.cfm?PubID=639 | archivedate =2014-01-06 | deadurl =no }}</ref>。联邦和州的调查人员要求《[[美国医学会杂志|美国医学会杂志]]》在之后12年以内都不要披露此次事件的细节信息，以防这些内容引发[[模仿犯罪|模仿犯罪]]，《美国医学会杂志》同意了这一要求<ref name="garrett" />。之后没有出现同类的攻击事件或[[恶作剧|恶作剧]]，对事件和调查过程的详细描述于1997年发表在《美国医学会杂志》上<ref name="entis" /><ref name="torok">{{cite journal | author = T. J. Török, R. V. Tauxe, R. P. Wise, J. R. Livengood, R. Sokolow, S. Mauvais, K. A. Birkness, M. R. Skeels, J. M. Horan and L. R. Foster | title = A Large Community Outbreak of Salmonellosis Caused by Intentional Contamination of Restaurant Salad Bars | journal = Journal of the American Medical Association | volume = 278 | issue = 5 | pages = 389-395 | date = 1997-08-06 | url = http://jama.jamanetwork.com/article.aspx?articleid=417893 | accessdate = 2014-02-20 | doi = 10.1001/jama.278.5.389 | pmid = 9244330 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131002221111/http://jama.jamanetwork.com/article.aspx?articleid=417893 | archivedate = 2013-10-02 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | last =Advisory Panel to Assess Domestic Response Capabilities for Terrorism Involving Weapons of Mass Destruction | title =Assessing The Threat: First Annual Report to The President and The Congress of the Advisory Panel to Assess Domestic Response Capabilities for Terrorism Involving Weapons of Mass Destruction | publisher =DIANE Publishing | date =1999-12-15 | pages =18-19 | archivedate =2010-07-03 | deadurl =no | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20100703023610/http://biotech.law.lsu.edu/blaw/general/terror.pdf | url =http://biotech.law.lsu.edu/blaw/general/terror.pdf | format =PDF | isbn =1-4289-8112-8 | accessdate =2014-02-20 }}</ref>。1999年，美国疾病控制与预防中心在《新发传染病》（{{lang|en|''Emerging Infectious Diseases''}}）上发表了一篇实证分析文章，其中说明了生物恐怖主义关联的六个激励因素，分别是：领袖魅力，没有外来选区的干扰，[[世界末日|世界末日]]意识形态，单独或分裂的团体，以及侵略性质的防卫方式<ref name="tuckercdc">{{cite journal | doi =10.3201/eid0504.990406 | last =Tucker | first =Jonathan B. | title =Historical Trends Related to Bioterrorism: An Empirical Analysis | journal =Emerging Infectious Diseases | volume =5 | issue =4 | pages =498-504 | publisher =Centers for Disease Control and Prevention | date =1999-07-01 | url =http://wwwnc.cdc.gov/eid/content/5/4/contents.htm | accessdate =2014-02-20 | pmid =10458952 | pmc =2627752 | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20140117003550/http://wwwnc.cdc.gov/eid/content/5/4/contents.htm | archivedate =2014-01-17 | deadurl =yes }}</ref>。根据这篇文章中的看法，“罗杰尼希邪教”满足除“世界末日意识”外的所有激励因素<ref name="tuckercdc" />。《邪教，宗教与暴力》（{{lang|en|''Cults, Religion and Violence''}}）一书的分析对[[魅力型权威|领袖魅力]]的看法表示异议，指出在这起事件以及其他的一些案例中，都是组织的副手在引发暴力行为上发挥了举足轻重的作用<ref name="bromley" />。作者认为，与人格魅力相比，社会关系往往是更具决定性的要素，即使是有一位很有魅力的领袖，要产生这样的结果，通常也需要有更为复杂的社会关系土壤<ref name="bromley">{{cite book | last1=Bromley | first1= David G. | last2=Melton | first2=J. Gordon | title =Cults, Religion and Violence | url=https://archive.org/details/cultsreligionvio00brom_016 | publisher =Cambridge University Press | date =2002-05-13 | page =[https://archive.org/details/cultsreligionvio00brom_016/page/n68 47] | isbn = 0-521-66898-0}}</ref>。

