dead-url =no }}</ref>。2005年，俄勒冈州土地委员会同意将沃斯科县包括奥修庄园城在内的1.9[[平方公里|平方公里]]土地卖给来自[[科罗拉多州|科罗拉多州]]的青年团体“年轻生命”（{{lang|en|Young Life}}）<ref name="oregonagrees">{{cite news | last =Associated Press | title =Oregon agrees to sell former Rajneeshees cult encampment | work =The Seattle Times | publisher =The Seattle Times Company | date =2005-12-15 | url =http://seattletimes.com/html/localnews/2002685608_webrajneeshees15.html | accessdate =2014-02-20 | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20131204175059/http://seattletimes.com/html/localnews/2002685608_webrajneeshees15.html | archivedate =2013-12-04 | deadurl =no }}</ref><ref name="katu">{{cite news | last =Staff | title =State agrees to sell former Rajneesh encampment | url =http://www.katu.com/news/3649031.html | work =KATU 2 Portland | date =2005-12-15 | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20140220025422/http://www.katu.com/news/3649031.html | archivedate =2014-02-20 | deadurl =no | accessdate =2014-02-20 }}</ref>。2005年2月18日，法庭频道播出了一期针对这起事件的《[[法医档案|法医档案]]》（{{lang|en|''Forensic Files''}}）节目，标题为《‘生物攻击’——俄勒冈州邪教投毒》（{{lang|en|'''Bio-Attack' – Oregon Cult Poisonings''}}）<ref>{{cite news | last =Staff | title ='Bio-Attack' – Oregon Cult Poisonings: In 1984, hundreds of people in The Dalles, Oregon became ill with food poisoning. Local, state and federal disease detectives slowly unraveled the medical mystery. Along with a unique strain of bacteria, they discovered a religious cult's bizarre plot to overthrow the government using germ warfare | work =Forensic Files: Court TV | publisher =Turner Entertainment Digital Network, Inc. | date =2005-02-18}}</ref>。媒体上还对这起沙门氏菌疫情与美国移民及归化局有关的联系进行了探讨<ref>{{cite news | last =Staff | title =Spinach scare sparks memories of The Dalles | work =Nashua Telegraph | publisher =Telegraph Publishing Company | date =2006-09-21}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url =http://www.ocala.com/article/20060923/OPINION/209230349 | last =Staff | title =Spinach and bioterrorism prevention | work =Ocala Star-Banner | date =2006-09-23 | accessdate =2014-02-20 | archivedate =2014-02-20 | deadurl =no | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20140220030837/http://www.ocala.com/article/20060923/OPINION/209230349 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | last =Staff | title =Bioterror and spinach | work =Scripps Howard News Service | date =2006-09-19 |url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=2202&dat=20060921&id=SZclAAAAIBAJ&sjid=gPQFAAAAIBAJ&pg=6745,2290569 |accessdate=2014-02-20}}</ref>。

